    "client_msg_id": "3c141b85-258a-43d7-8dfa-b69d8eedaa78",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "I can tell you that Teslas freak out over a lot less than a balloon.  It's a lot less of an \"autopilot\" than mixed initiative automatically adjusting autonomous system.  I haven't used those words in a long time.  <https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Dimensions-of-Adjustable-Autonomy-and-Interaction-Bradshaw-Feltovich/e4bfe3b40d36f0b8c79c4c98319d4bf51569d080>",
    "user": "UA14TGLTC",
    "ts": "1633693663.287700",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
